    ~~~~~~~~~~
    simplequiz
    ~~~~~~~~~~
    
    Simple Module that enables one to play a quiz like those typical
    quizshows on TV.

    I was inspired by some question at python-forum.de:
        
        http://www.python-forum.de/viewtopic.php?f=18&t=28985
    
    and by a proposal I made in this thread at ubuntuusers.de:
        
        http://forum.ubuntuusers.de/topic/python-2-oder-/4/#post-3409942
